    new "朱莉安娜会因为对你的论文评价过严而道歉，然后邀请你和她一起学习。"

    # game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:3
    old "She will be at Cafe Skyhill on a weekday morning. Study with her a few times to get this scene."
    new "她会在工作日的早上出现在Skyhill咖啡馆。和她一起学习几次就能解锁这个场景。"

    # game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:20
